Package vooga.towerdefense.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GameLoop
    This class represents a game loop.
    GameMap
    The GameMap holds all of the state corresponding to an entire game at a given moment, including all towers and units and the tiles that comprise the map itself.
    GameModel
    GameModel holds all of the state and behavior for a particular game of towerdefense
    Path
    Used to help units move through the map, a Path is a list of points that a Unit can follow in a sequence using the FollowPath action.
    Pathfinder
    Generates paths based on what tiles are eligible to walk on in the map using graph algorithms.
    Player
    A player object, which holds things like score and lives.
    Tile
    This class represents a Tile object.
